---
title: Parmesan Panko Chicken Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: With just five minutes of prep and a hands-free turn in the oven, you'll have this baked Parmesan-crusted chicken on the table in no time. For sides, we've got steamed broccoli, crunchy garlic bread, and ranch dressing for dipping. But the best part? Thanks to the oven-ready tray included with your ingredients, there’s practically no cleanup required.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67325ab51cd01ca44ffc2bd0-c53b0590.jpeg
